lead_paragraph: TRIPLER HALL.--Fourth Concert by Catharine Hayes. Doors open at 7. BROUGHAM'S.--The Actress of Padna and 'The Rough Diamond', Doors open at 7. BOWERY.--'Damon and Pythias,' Mr. Mrs. White' and 'The Miller and his Men.' Doors open at 7. NIBLO'S.--'Crown Diamonds', Doors open at 7. BURTON'S.--'The Stranger' and 'The Honeymoon.' Doors open at 7.
